title: DIRECTV by EnterSource / NewsRadio WGNS Week 6 Awards Presented
text:
DIRECTV by EnterSource / NewsRadio WGNS Week 6 Awards Presented Published: September 29, 2015 (L-R: Casey Perkins, Andy DeGraw, head coach Matt Williams) 
Smyrna High School was last week's DIRECTV by EnterSource / NewsRadio WGNS "Game of the Week" recipient. 
Andy DeGraw, Vice President of DIRECTV by EnterSource, presented a plaque to the Bulldogs Tuesday after their 45-7 win over Siegel last Friday night. 
The game's MVP was running back Casey Perkins. He had 134 yards on 16 carries and four touchdowns...all in the first half. He had all but 76 yards of the Bulldogs total rushing yards. Related Articles
